			<Fragment slot="hero-para">One of the UK's foremost woollen yarn spinners with a world-wide reputation for excellence.</Fragment>
		</Hero>

		<PageContentSection heading="The Home Page" bgColour="var(--lightbluegrey)">
			<Fragment slot="page-content">
				<p>Here is some content for the home page, it's not really about anything. It's ultimately meaningless. Stop reading, it's a waste of time.</p>
