			</Fragment>

			<Fragment slot="page-content-2">
				<p>Oh look! A whole new column of content to not read.</p>
				<p>Lorem ipsum dolor, sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Blanditiis fugiat quaerat, maxime beatae illum molestias libero odit! Enim repudiandae, facilis dignissimos nulla amet nam ratione.</p>
